<h2 class="bac">Summary:</h2>
<ul class="bac">
	<li>Locations: Opportunities across EMEA</li>
	<li>9-week programme from June &#45; August</li>
	<li>Strong A-level grades and on track for a minimum 2:1 degree (or equivalent)</li>
	<li>Second language required for some roles</li>
